    "description": "FM Logistic India Global Group, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Supply Chain Manager for our Pimpri-Chinchwad operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout FM Logistic India Global Group:\nFM Logistic India Global Group is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with FM Logistic India Global Group!",
